page.title: 12YOUTH CULTURE
page.content: The fashion at the moment is trainers and tracksuit.Some trainers are-Nike, Adidas,Puma,Olympus.You can get Adidas Nike,Puma,Olympus,Fila and Sergio Tacchinie tracksuits.Cagoules are in fashion today,here are some types -Kappa,Fila,Adidas,Nike,Puma and Olympus. Everybody is into Breaking,here are some moves-buffalo walk,headspin, handspin and kneespin.Body Popping is similar to Breaking.Electric Funk is the in music just now,here are some more kinds of music-Electros 1-719 by Paul Hardcastle. The letters B.M.X. stand for Bicycle- Moto-Cross(X).These are some good B.M.X. bikes-Diamond Back,Haro Freestyler,Mag Burner and Super Tuff Burner. These are some examples of today's fashion.
